snippet.textDisplay:
1/10 Today I'm going to talk about Brave Browser (BB). Today changes the way you use your web / mobile browser. www.brave.com/cal137

2/10 Brave blocks ads and trackers (cookies). Its users are anonymous. YouTube videos start playing one at a time without having to see ads. When you google "flight to Miami" you don't see ads for "Miami" for 6 months.

3/10 Other browsers claim to have "private mode", but only hide the search history. Brave allows you to use Tor directly. Tor not only hides history, it hides geographic location and uses encrypted connection to be anonymous. https://brave.com/cal137

4/10 On a PC, BB loads twice (2x) faster than Chrome / Firefox. On mobile it loads up to eight times (8x) faster than Chrome / Firefox. At the end of the month one ends up saving data since one doesn’t load the websites PLUS the ads that each website has. In other words, GBs are saved from the data plan.

5/10 Fun fact: One of the Brave developers is Brendan Eich, Inventor of JavaScript and co-founder of Mozilla. Great dude! www.brave.com/cal137

6/10 Users usually pay to browse by viewing ads. They spend time and data downloading ad technology that transmits their data to advertisers. Brave is the new Internet. Now time is valued, personal data is kept private and ATTENTION is rewarded.

7/10 Brave allows you to activate non-invasive ads. Depending on the # of ads and geographic location one receives rewards in the form of crypto. BAT (Basic Attention Token) is the one used by Brave. It can be exchanged for Bitcoin to buy online or exchange for dollars, euros, etc. www.brave.com/cal137

8/10 Brave is based on Chromium, which is the open source engine that also runs Google Chrome and Microsoft Edge. For that reason, you can add all Chrome extensions to Brave.

9/10 Brave allows you to reward users on Twitter, Youtube, Reddit and other platforms. When using BB for desktop you will see a tip button on every tweet, video or post. Tap the tip button to send it directly to the author. https://brave.com/cal137

10/10. ALL my friends and family who downloaded Brave ended up deleting Google Chrome and other apps. Brave is free, fast, ad-free and secure. Download link: https://brave.com/cal137
